H.B. 260
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
Mar 3, 2025
SESSION 2025
HOUSE PRINCIPAL CLERK
H D
HOUSE BILL DRH10104-MHa-43
Short Title: Reallocate Raeford Sewer Infrastructure Funds. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative G. Pierce.
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO ALLOW ADDITIONAL USES FOR CERTAIN FUNDS ALLOCATED TO THE
3 CITY OF RAEFORD.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. Subsection 4.2(g) of S.L. 2024-1 reads as rewritten:
6 "SECTION 4.2.(g) Of the funds allocated to the City of Raeford by Section 12.2(e)(145) of
7 S.L. 2023-134, three million dollars ($3,000,000) shall be used for the extension of sewer lines
8 to the Cameron Heights community.community or for any other water or wastewater project."
9 SECTION 2. This act is effective when it becomes law.
*DRH10104-MHa-43*

